<F P=100> CHINA </F>
<H3> <TI>   Narcotics Dealers, Addicts Punished in Yingkou City </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Narcotics Dealers, Addicts Punished in Yingkou City </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   SK0406093894 Shenyang LIAONING RIBAO in Chinese 25 May 94 p 1 </F>
<F P=103> SK0406093894 </F>
<F P=104>  Shenyang LIAONING RIBAO </F>
<F P=105>  Chinese </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] On 17 May, Yingkou city held an open trial to 
punish a group of narcotics dealers and addicts. It was 
announced five heroin dealers were to be arrested according to 
the law, 16 dolantinum dealers were to undergo labor 
reeducation, and 19 persons addicted to narcotics were forced to 
give up taking narcotics. 

</TEXT>

