<H3> <TI>   More Than 1,000 Kg of Marijuana Bound for Coahuila Seized </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    More Than 1,000 Kg of Marijuana Bound for Coahuila Seized </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   94WB0042C Mexico City EXCELSIOR in Spanish 17 May 94 p 7-A-3 </F>
<F P=103> 94WB0042C </F>
<F P=104>  Mexico City EXCELSIOR </F>
<F P=105>  Spanish </F>


