<F P=102>   AU0906102294 Cologne Deutschlandfunk Network in German 0900 
GMT 9 Jun 94 </F>

<F P=103> AU0906102294 </F>
<F P=104>  Cologne Deutschlandfunk Network </F>
<F P=105>  German </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] A special commission of the Bavarian Land Office of 
Criminal Investigation [LKA] has crushed an international drug 
ring. A spokesman for the LKA said in Munich today, that in a 
large-scale operation in Munich, Hamburg, Duesseldorf, and 
Nuremberg earlier this week, police apprehended 14 Germans and 
Turks. They are suspected of having imported tons of heroin to 
Spain, Italy, and Germany. The spokesman added that another 10 
persons were arrested in northern Italy and Spain. In the 
operation, the officials also detected comprehensive money 
laundering practices. 

</TEXT>

</DOC>

