<H4>    Thai Court Hears Conflicting Stories </H4>

<F P=102> 94WD0381B London THE DAILY TELEGRAPH in English 17 May 94 p 
14--FOR OFFICIAL USE ONLY </F>

<F P=103> 94WD0381B </F>
<F P=104>  London THE DAILY TELEGRAPH </F>
