<H4>    `Big Increase' in Arrests in France </H4>

<F P=102> 94WD0381C London THE TIMES in English 17 May 94 p 8--FOR 
OFFICIAL USE ONLY </F>

<F P=103> 94WD0381C </F>
<F P=104>  London THE TIMES </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


