<H3> <TI>   Narcotics Discovered on St. Petersburg-Tallinn Train </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Narcotics Discovered on St. Petersburg-Tallinn Train </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   WS1306093494 Tallinn ETA in English 1606 GMT 10 Jun 94 </F>
<F P=103> WS1306093494 </F>
<F P=104>  Tallinn ETA </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

<F P=106> ["News Release"] </F>
  [Text] Russian customs authorities discovered a large 
amount of narcotics, worth about 25 thousand USD, in 
St.Petersburg-Tallinn train Friday morning. 
  During a regular customs check at the Ivangorod border 
station, the Russian customs authorities found eleven packages 
of "grayish-yellow powdery substance" under luggage shelves 
mattresses. Questioning of travellers and train conductors did 
not reveal a possible suspect. 

</TEXT>

