<H3> <TI>   FELCN Department Chief Rejects Extradition of Jose Luis </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    FELCN Department Chief Rejects Extradition of Jose Luis </PHRASE></F></HT>


<TEXT>
Seleme   to U.S. 

<F P=102> PY1006002594 La Paz LA RAZON in Spanish 1 Jun 94 p A13 </F>
<F P=103> PY1006002594 </F>
<F P=104>  La Paz LA RAZON </F>
<F P=105>  Spanish </F>
BFN 

  [Excerpt] Cochabamba, 1 June (ANF) -- Colonel Hugo 
Guarachi, Special Antinarcotics Force (FELCN) department 
commander, has rejected the possible extradition to the United 
States of Jose Luis Seleme, the owner of several night clubs and 
an alleged drug trafficker. 
  Recent reports in Cochabamba have stated that Seleme's 
working capital totals at least $7 million. FELCN personnel 
arrested Seleme at dawn on 27 May for his ties with 
international drug trafficking rings. [passage omitted] 

</TEXT>

