<H3> <TI>   Antidrug Brigade Destroys 268 Kg of Cocaine </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Antidrug Brigade Destroys 268 Kg of Cocaine </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   FL1706222994 Port-au-Prince Radio Metropole in FRench 1600 
GMT 17 Jun 94 </F>

<F P=103> FL1706222994 </F>
<F P=104>  Port-au-Prince Radio Metropole </F>
<F P=105>  FRench </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Excerpt] The Haitian anti-drug service, on 16 June, in the 
presence of journalists, destroyed 268 kilos of cocaine from 
Colombia, intended for the U.S. market. The cocaine, seized 
during recent months by the Haitian anti-drug brigade, was 
thrown in the sea offshore by a unit of the Haitian Navy, aboard 
which were journalists and photographers who were invited to 
cover the event. [passage omitted] 

</TEXT>

